    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Top hats made of beaver fur or of a fabric simulating this fur. Prefer "castors (hats)" for other men's hats of beaver fur made in varying form.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
